title: maiden england
content:

thanx in advance

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018114718im_/http:/typophile.com/files/Imagem2_5427.jpg)
author: rockberto

comments.content:
It looks like a heavy/bold weight of Futura like e.g. **[Futura EF (Heavy)](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018114718/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Berthold&ffam=Futura%20BQ%20-%20DemiBold&fid=2ac4215f0756be144108c5af278a0551&fsize=60&text=MAIDEN%20ENGLAND%20'88&fit=1)**  
The "dust & scratches" effect is probably added later (same letters contain different scratch patterns).

-----------------------------------------------  
I found it using Find my Font - [http://www.findmyfont.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018114718/http:/www.findmyfont.com/ "http://www.findmyfont.com")
